Package: ERASE
Type: Package
Title: Extended Randomization for Assessment of Multiple Annotation Enrichment in ASE Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Karishma D'Sa
Maintainer: Karishma D'Sa <karishma.m.dsa@gmail.com>
Description: The ERASE package assesses the enrichment of ASE sites in single
    or multiple annotation datasets using a randomization based approach 
    that accounts for read depth, an important bias in ASE detection
